Contains:

Va.Udo.Crm.Scripts.Popup.MsgBox(text,style,title) returns jquery deferred object
Va.Udo.Crm.Scripts.Popup.InputBox(prompt,defaultValue,title) returns jquery deferred object
Va.Udo.Crm.Scripts.Popup.Popup(prompt,content,options) returns jquery deferred object

Deferred data for .done and .fail
data (argument 1) = {
    Clicked: {
        Name: "Name of the Button",
        ButtonType: Va.Udo.Crm.Scripts.PopupButtonTypes number
    },
    Values: collection of values returned from input, select, or textara in a InputBox or Popup
    {
        popupText: value for default InputBox
    }
}

Enums:
Va.Udo.Crm.Scripts.Popup.ButtonTypes: return for button clicked type
{
        Ok:1,
        Cancel:2,
        Abort:3,
        Retry:4,
        Ignore:5,
        Yes:6,
        No:7
}

Va.Udo.Crm.Scripts.Popup.PopupStyles is an enum with what buttons to include and the visual style of the popup:
{
        OKOnly: 0,
        OKCancel: 1,
        AbortRetryIgnore: 2,
        YesNoCancel: 3,
        YesNo: 4,
        RetryCancel: 5,
        Normal: 0,
        Critical: 16,
        Question: 32,
        Exclamation: 48,
        Information: 64,
        DefaultButton1: 0,
        DefaultButton2: 256,
        DefaultButton3: 512
}

requirements
- Only one control can be inserted on the form.
- this control should be put as web resource in the first tab.  The nameof the tab needs to be "displaytabs".  There shouldn't be any other fields present in the tab or section.
- there has to be minimum of another tab with other fields on the form.
- Hidden tabs should start with "~hid~"  for example "~hid~ Hidden Fields"
